snippet.title: Blades of Time (Nintendo Switch) Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Blades of Time, the time-warping Hack ’n’ Slash action adventure featuring fast-paced combat with swords, firearms and magic, is now heading for a launch on Nintendo Switch on May 14.

• Official website: http://www.bladesoftime.com/
